ser%20base%2C%26quot%3B%20Feingold%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20also%20they%20come%20back%20to%20the%20product%20a%20lot.%20It's%20so%20tied%20to%20what%20they%20are%20using%20the%20internet%20for%2C%20which%20is%20research%2C%20studying%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20knowledge%20work%20that%20Perplexity%20is%20built%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20March%202024%2C%20Perplexity%20had%20around%2015%20million%20monthly%20active%20users%3B%20it%20declined%20to%20give%20a%20more%20recent%20user%20total.%20The%20company%20was%20last%20valued%20at%20around%20%249%20billion%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-ai-valuation-funding-500-million-9-billion-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efunding%20round%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20by%20IVP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20of%20Harvard%2C%20MIT%2C%20and%20Northeastern%20post%20for%20a%20photo%20during%20a%20Perplexity%20campus%20event.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a63546bfebcc4d029e3362%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20Yang%2C%20an%20engineering%20lead%20at%20Perplexity%2C%20spoke%20to%20college%20students%20from%20across%20Boston%20at%20a%20Future%20of%20Search%20campus%20event.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Aditya%20Agarwal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20a%20viral%20app%20all%20but%20requires%20buy-in%20from%20teens%2C%20tweens%2C%20and%20twenty-somethings.%20By%20now%2C%20most%20of%20them%20have%20heard%20of%20ChatGPT.%20It's%20been%20over%20two%20years%20since%20the%20chatbot's%20public%20launch%20dazzled%20the%20tech%20world.%20And%20the%20use%20of%20ChatGPT%20is%20ticking%20up%2C%20particularly%20among%20younger%20people.%20About%20a%20quarter%20of%20American%20teens%20say%20they've%20used%20ChatGPT%20for%20schoolwork%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2025%2F01%2F15%2Fabout-a-quarter-of-us-teens-have-used-chatgpt-for-schoolwork-double-the-share-in-2023%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20in%20the%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnlisting%20students%20allows%20ChatGPT's%20rivals%20to%20reach%20trendsetters%20who%20have%20access%20to%20thousands%20of%20other%20students%20through%20their%20dorms%2C%20mailing%20lists%2C%20private%20WhatsApp%20groups%2C%20and%20classes.%20This%20strategy%20mirrors%20the%20tactics%20used%20by%20iconic%20apps%20like%20Facebook%2C%20Snapchat%2C%20and%20Tinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20generation%20that%20has%20grown%20up%20with%20tech%20in%20their%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Emma%20Yee%20Yick%2C%20global%20community%20lead%20at%20startup%20Notion%2C%20where%20she's%20run%20a%20campus%20ambassador%20program%20these%20past%20three%20years.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20now%20they're%20in%20college%2C%20and%20they%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20going%20to%20decide%20what%20tools%20we%20use%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fbb23da6-01f8-49cc-b77e-413d5587eca3%5C%22%3EChatGPT%2C%20but%20better%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELiner%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20search%20engines%20you've%20never%20heard%20of.%20With%20over%2010%20million%20users%20globally%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fa16z.com%2F100-gen-ai-apps%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndreessen%20Horowitz%3C%2Fa%3E%20recognized%20it%20as%20the%20fourth-most%20widely%20used%20generative%20AI%20web%20product%20last%20year.%20The%20app%20works%20similarly%20to%20Perplexity%20but%20instead%20of%20combing%20large%20swaths%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20it%20narrows%20its%20search%20to%20credible%20sources%20like%20academic%20papers%20and%20government%20databases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20a%20South%20Korean%20startup%2C%20Liner's%20name%20barely%20registers%20outside%20some%20higher%20education%20circles.%20The%20company's%20campus%20ambassador%20program%20aims%20to%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20crowd%20forms%20around%20a%20Liner%20table%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ab9f30eb4be2fff9a449e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20crowd%20forms%20around%20a%20Liner%20table%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kristine%20Zhou%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20week%2C%20Kristine%20Zhou%2C%20a%20sophomore%20and%20Liner%20ambassador%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20hangs%20outside%20the%20student%20center%20with%20a%20laptop%20and%20a%20party%20tray%20of%20Chick-fil-A.%20She%20offers%20demos%20to%20students%20passing%20by%2C%20reeling%20them%20in%20with%20free%20chicken%20sandwiches.%20But%20the%20real%20hook%2C%20said%20Zhou%2C%20is%20Liner's%20focus%20on%20providing%20users%20with%20reliable%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20program%20kicked%20off%20last%20semester%20at%20four%20California%20universities%2C%20which%20the%20company%20picked%20for%20their%20proximity%20to%20Liner%20employees%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20said%20Alex%20Yoon%2C%20head%20of%20US%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Perplexity%2C%20student%20evangelists%20focus%20on%20practical%20applications%20when%20tabling%20on%20the%20quad%20or%20speaking%20to%20a%20club.%20Arthita%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20graduate%20student%20at%20Chicago%20Booth%20in%20London%20on%20an%20exchange%20term%2C%20engages%20students%20by%20asking%20about%20their%20travel%20plans.%20She%20uses%20the%20app%20to%20swiftly%20generate%20a%20two-day%20itinerary%20with%20must-see%20attractions%2C%20travel%20times%2C%20and%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsis%20Decrem%2C%20a%20computer%20science%20major%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%2C%20emphasizes%20the%20versatility%20of%20Perplexity.%20She%20demonstrates%20the%20ability%20to%20switch%20between%20models%20within%20the%20app%20to%20vary%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221187%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arthita%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20graduate%20student%20and%20Perplexity%20ambassador%20at%20Chicago%20Booth%2C%20holds%20a%20cash%20prize%20during%20a%20Perplexity%20pitch%20contest.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a61f7feb4be2fff9a3e860%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22890%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EArthita%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20graduate%20student%20and%20Perplexity%20ambassador%20at%20Chicago%20Booth%2C%20holds%20a%20cash%20prize%20during%20a%20pitch%20contest.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Arthita%20Ghosh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou.com%20is%20also%20in%20the%20business%20of%20search%20but%20doesn't%20call%20itself%20a%20search%20engine.%20Founded%20by%20two%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-exec-richard-socher-youcom-harvard-business-review-ai-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStanford%20machine%20learning%20researchers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company%20makes%20a%20digital%20workspace%20for%20conducting%20research%2C%20creating%20content%2C%20and%20building%20custom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-ai-agents-raising-venture-funding-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagents%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20perform%20tasks%20on%20their%20own.%20To%20help%20grow%20its%20foothold%2C%20You.com%20leverages%20campus%20ambassadors%20at%2018%20universities%2C%20including%20Stanford%2C%20New%20York%20University%2C%20and%20Georgia%20Tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVishal%20Makhijani%2C%20You.com's%20chief%20operating%20officer%2C%20notes%20that%20if%20the%20program%20works%20as%20it%20should%2C%20the%20company%20should%20see%20benefits%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou.com%20is%20trying%20to%20be%20the%20leading%20productivity%20platform%20for%20knowledge%20workers%2C%20and%20college%20students%20are%20just%20knowledge%20workers%20in%20a%20year%20or%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Makhijani%2C%20who%20was%20the%20longtime%20chief%20executive%20of%20online%20education%20company%20Udacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20loyal%20users%20might%20continue%20using%20You.com%20in%20their%20first%20jobs%2C%20streamlining%20the%20company's%20efforts%20to%20sell%20into%20organizations%20and%20shortening%20sales%20cycles%2C%20said%20Makhijani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c0826db-e475-48b2-a195-889fa5ae992a%5C%22%3EGoodies%20and%20goodwill%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20unspoken%20goal%20of%20competitors%20in%20this%20market%20is%20to%20secure%20a%20second-place%20finish.%20Google%20is%20the%20dominant%20search%20engine%2C%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Ftopics%2F1710%2Fsearch-engine-usage%2F%23topicOverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E90%25%20share%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20global%20search%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20startups%20may%20not%20dethrone%20Google%20as%20the%20go-to%20search%20engine%2C%20their%20efforts%20are%20far%20from%20futile%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20student%20ambassadors%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20position%20is%20usually%20unpaid%20(Liner%20pays%20students%20%2420%20an%20hour)%2C%20the%20student%20ambassador%C2%A0will%20likely%20benefit%20from%20free%20subscriptions%2C%20logo%20apparel%2C%20virtual%20events%20with%20company%20leaders%2C%20and%20the%20opportunity%20to%20link%20their%20name%20with%20a%20buzzy%20startup.%20In%20today's%20frozen%20job%20market%2C%20many%20students%20believe%20working%20as%20a%20campus%20ambassador%20helps%20bridge%20the%20gap%20to%20their%20ideal%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity%20saw%20an%20over%20600%25%20increase%20in%20applications%20for%20its%20spring%20semester%20program%20compared%20to%20the%20fall%2C%20according%20to%20Feingold%2C%20Perplexity's%20community