ession's%20traditional%20practices%20and%20lack%20of%20uniform%20safety%20precautions%20may%20have%20contributed.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration%20and%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-cutting-dei-activist-backlash-harley-davidson-deere-tractor-supply-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajor%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-equal-employment-opportunity-act-explained-dei-businesses-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erolling%20back%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20may%20benefit%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20highlight%20the%20nuanced%2C%20layered%20reality%20of%20being%20a%20woman%20real-estate%20agent%2C%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20four%20brokers%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20They%20candidly%20shared%20their%20experiences%2C%20which%20included%20being%20undermined%20by%20male%20colleagues%20and%20feeling%20unsafe%20during%20showings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20hear%20from%20the%20agents%20in%20their%20own%20words%2C%20though%20their%20reflections%20have%20been%20lightly%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBess%20Freedman%2C%2055%2C%20CEO%20of%20Brown%20Harris%20Stevens%20in%20New%20York%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223126%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bess%20Freedman's%20headshot%2C%20sitting%20on%20a%20counter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a4c73c7bb3f854015bf769%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224689%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFreedman%20has%20been%20in%20real%20estate%20for%20over%2020%20years.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Bess%20Freedman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20becoming%20Brown%20Harris%20Stevens's%20CEO%2C%20I%20was%20an%20agent%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20I%20quickly%20learned%20that%20you%20have%20to%20hustle%20twice%20as%20hard%20as