22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a4c71cbfebcc4d029dfe4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224256%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrews%20works%20at%20Realty%20ONE%20Group%20Next%20Generation.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Danielle%20Andrews%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20middle%20school%20social%20studies%20teacher%20when%20I%20first%20got%20my%20real-estate%20license.%20I've%20been%20in%20the%20industry%20for%20nine%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20I%20only%20planned%20to%20do%20real%20estate%20part-time%20to%20supplement%20teaching%20%E2%80%94%20just%20summers%20and%20a%20little%20extra%20income.%20However%2C%20I%20discovered%20my%20passion%20for%20it%20and%20have%20been%20fully%20immersed%20in%20the%20industry%20since%202016.%20I%20opened%20my%20own%20brokerage%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavigating%20the%20industry%20as%20a%20woman%20has%20meant%20balancing%20breaking%20stereotypes%20and%20maintaining%20authenticity.%20It's%20been%20a%20whirlwind%20journey%20%E2%80%94%20not%20easy%2C%20but%20incredibly%20rewarding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20average%20profile%20of%20real%20estate%20agents%20is%20female%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20male-dominated%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20related%20fields%20like%20inspections%2C%20construction%2C%20and%20development.%20I've%20lost%20count%20of%20how%20often%20a%20contractor%20or%20client%20has%20tried%20to%20%26quot%3Bman-splain%26quot%3B%20something%20I'm%20already%20well-versed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20experiences%20where%20I've%20spoken%20to%20male%20inspectors%20or%20contractors%2C%20and%20they'll%20say%20things%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20you%20don't%20or%20wouldn't%20know%20anything%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20they%20try%20to%20speak%20above%20me%20%E2%80%94%20as%20if%20we're%20not%20colleagues%20and%20on%20the%20same%20level.%20Those%20moments%20have%20taught%20me%20the%20value%20of%20preparation%20and%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESafety%20is%20another%20critical%20aspect%20of%20this%20industry.%20As%20real-estate%20agents%2C%20we%20often%20meet%20new%20people%20in%20unfamiliar%20locations%2C%20so%20it's%20essential%20to%20prioritize%20our%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20sellers%20forget%20to%20secure%20weapons%20or%20belongings%2C%20and%20occasionally%2C%20sellers'%20agents%20fail%20to%20communicate%20that%20the%20seller%20will%20still%20be%20home%20during%20a%20showing.%20Entering%20someone's%20home%20can%20be%20alarming%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20people%20may%20react%20out%20of%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20learned%20to%20always%20share%20my%20location%20with%20a%20trusted%20person%2C%20along%20with%20the%20name%20and%20details%20of%20the%20person%20I'm%20meeting.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20I've%20learned%20to%20trust%20my%20instincts.%20If%20something%20feels%20off%2C%20I%20take%20precautions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20do%20some%20due%20diligence%2C%20especially%20if%20I%20get%20a%20gut%20feeling%20that%20something%20isn't%20quite%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20benefit%20through%20our%20local%20board%20association%20called%20Forewarn.%20It's%20an%20app%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20search%20for%20someone%20by%20name%20or%20phone%20number%20and%20shows%20their%20criminal%20history%20and%20public%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20tend%20to%20do%20research%20on%20social%20media%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eif%20I'm%20unsure%20about%20someone%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20weren't%20referred%20to%20me%20by%20a%20family%20member%20or%20someone%20I%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20something%20still%20seems%20off%2C%20my%20last%20two%20measures%20are%20to%20take%20another%20agent%20with%20me%20%E2%80%94%20preferably%20a%20male.%20Sometimes%2C%20my%20husband%20has%20come%20along%20to%20showings%20for%20added%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20transaction%20is%20worth%20compromising%20your%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELindsey%20Harn%2C%2038%2C%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20in%20San%20Luis%20Obispo%2C%20California%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lindsey%20Harn's%20headshot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a61cda7bb3f854015c2566%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221281%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarn%20works%20at%20Christie's%20International%20Real%20Estate.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lindsey%20Harn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20real%20estate%20because%20I%20believe%20there%20is%20endless%20potential%20for%20all%20agents%20regardless%20of%20their%20education%2C%20socioeconomic%20status%2C%20gender%2C%20or%20sexual%20orientation.%20You%20don't%20need%20a%20fancy%20degree%20if%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20ways%2C%20I%20think%20being%20a%20woman%20in%20this%20business%20is%20a%20huge%20advantage.%20Buying%20or%20selling%20a%20home%20is%20someone's%20biggest%20investment%20and%20can%20be%20very%20emotional%20for%20both%20the%20buyer%20and%20seller.%20Women%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20softer%2C%20more%20sensitive%2C%20and%20more%20detail-oriented%20regarding%20homebuying%20and%20selling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20having%20entered%20the%20business%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20I%20know%20that%20older%20men%20sometimes%20view%20younger%20women%20as%20weak%20or%20unknowledgeable%20enough%20to%20enter%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20when%20I%20was%20about%2022%2C%20I%20came%20to%20a%20showing%20with%20a%20local%20attorney%2C%20and%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20god%2C%20you're%20the%20youngest%20real-estate%20agent%20I've%20ever%20seen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20time%2C%20while%20working%20with%20a%20male%20colleague%2C%20I%20had%20a%20client%20in%20his%2070s%20who%20was%20ready%20to%20make%20an%20offer.%20You%20could%20tell%20he%20wasn't%20comfortable%20discussing%20finances%20or%20finalizing%20the%20deal%20with%20a%20young%20woman.%20So%20he%20asked%20my%20business%20partner%20to%20step%20in%20for%20what%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20guess%20he%20considered%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Bmanly%26quot%3B%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20age%20and%20confidence%20grew%2C%20situations%20like%20this%20became%20less%20of%20a%20factor.%20But%20I%20definitely%20remember%20those%20moments%20when%20being%20young%20and%20female%20felt%20like%20a%20disadvantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMallory%20Bogard%2C%2039%2C%20a%20broker%20in%20New%20York%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mallory%20Bogard's%20headshot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a3d4f37bb3f854015be785%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBogard%20is%20the%20cofounder%20of%20The%20Bogard%20New%20York%20Team%20at%20Serhant.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mallory%20Bogard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20my%20real%20estate%20team%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%202020%20with%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20the%20unique%20perspective%20of%20running%20my%20company%20with%20a%20man%20by%20my%20side%2C%20which%20has%20really%20shed%20light%20on%20how%20people%20receive%20messages%20from%20men%20versus%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20can%20be%20just%20as%20capable%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20more%20capable%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20buy-in%20is%20often%20higher%20when%20a%20man%20says%20it.%20Men%20sometimes%20have%20an%20influence%20over%20people%20that%20women%20struggle%20to%20garner.%20I've%20witnessed%20how%20this%20plays%20out%20in%20business%20many%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20I%20can%20deliver%20the%20same%20message%20as%20my%20husband%2C%20but%20how%20it's%20received%20changes%20depending%20on%20who%20delivers%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20sometimes%2C%20we%20have%20to%20make%20recommendations%20that%20go%20against%20what%20our%20client%20wants.%20This%20could%20be%20about%20price%2C%20timeline%2C%20or%20entering%20a%20challenging%20market.%20We%20may%20need%20to%20deliver%20tough%20news%2C%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20you%20need%20this%20number%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20we'll%20be%20able%20to%20get%20it%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20husband%20delivers%20the%20bad%20news%2C%20clients%20are%20often%20more%20accepting%2C%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BOK%2C%20he's%20done%20everything%20he%20can.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20they%20feel%20I%20need%20to%20do%20more%20when%20I%20deliver%20the%20same%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20cognizant%20of%20removing%20emotion%20from%20message%20delivery.%20To%20be%20quite%20frank%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20have%20to%20provide%20more%20facts%20and%20do%20more%20research%20when%20having%20tough%20conversations%20than%20my%20husband%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20doing%20everything%20I%20can%20to%20teach%20the%20women%20on%20my%20team%20how%20to%20combat%20this%20double%20standard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconfessions-women-in-real-estate-female-agents-what-its-like-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739353502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ab6b90eb4be2fff9a43939%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconfessions-women-in-real-estate-female-agents-what-its-like-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recent%20accusations%20of%20misconduct%20have%20spotlighted%20how%20women%20in%20real%20estate%20are%20treated.%20Four%20brokers%20let%20us%20into%20their%20day-to-day%20lives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22alloyd%40insider.com%20(Alcynna%20Lloyd)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconfessions-women-in-real-estate-female-agents-what-its-like-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Monty%20the%20giant%20s