%3E%26quot%3BObsession%3A%20I%20think%20that's%20how%20you%20can%20summarize%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Brendan%20Gahan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20marketing%20agency%20Creator%20Authority.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20he%20can%20talk%20about%20YouTube%20and%20very%20little%20else.%20His%20knowledge%20base%20is%20not%20typical%20of%20most%20people's%3B%20it's%20very%20narrow%20and%20very%20deep.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonaldson's%20distaste%20for%20the%20conventions%20of%20big%20media%20companies%20has%20gotten%20him%20in%20trouble%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-mrbeast-embroiled-in-controversy-involving-staff-amazon-show-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccusations%20of%20poor%20conditions%20on%20MrBeast%20production%20sets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20internal%20staffer%20misconduct%20have%20created%20serious%20headaches%2C%20which%20the%20company%20recently%20sought%20to%20address%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FMrBeast%2Fstatus%2F1852410203486183777%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20internal%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20YouTuber%20scaled%20up%20so%20quickly%20by%20%26quot%3Bnot%20playing%20by%20the%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20one%20former%20staffer%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20But%20as%20traditional%20media%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-not-netflix-is-big-threat-to-hollywood-analysis-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elose%20eyeballs%20to%20user-generated-content%20platforms%20like%20YouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20TikTok%2C%20the%20MrBeast%20model%2C%20untamed%20as%20it%20is%2C%20can%20offer%20some%20useful%20lessons%20for%20Hollywood%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafter-beast-games-hollywood-wants-more-creator-influencer-tv-shows-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebring%20creators%20into%20traditional%20media%20productions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20give%20them%20a%20real%20stake%20in%20the%20work%2C%20allow%20them%20to%20be%20themselves%2C%20and%20produce%20content%20at%20a%20pace%20and%20style%20that%20feeds%20the%20appetites%20of%20digital%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20insight%20into%20the%20MrBeast%20empire%2C%20we%20talked%20with%20media%20executives%20both%20in%20Hollywood%20and%20at%20companies%20focused%20on%20creators%2C%20as%20well%20as%20people%20who%20have%20worked%20directly%20with%20Donaldson.%20We%20also%20combed%20through%20Donaldson's%20public%20statements%20and%20internal%20company%20documents%2C%20including%20a%20leaked%20MrBeast%20employee%20guidebook%20and%20163%20slides%20from%20a%20set%20of%20brand%20decks%20included%20in%20court%20filings.%20From%20our%20analysis%2C%20we%20landed%20on%20three%20key%20insights%20for%20traditional%20media%20companies%20trying%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20rapidly%20changing%20media%20landscape.%20MrBeast's%20style%20may%20not%20fit%20the%20tastes%20of%20Hollywood's%20elite%2C%20but%20they'd%20better%20start%20taking%20some%20notes%20on%20his%20successful%20strategies%20%E2%80%94%20or%20risk%20getting%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EMrBeast%20is%20perhaps%20the%20most%20visible%20face%20of%20the%20creator%20economy%2C%20a%20fast-growing%20subset%20of%20influencers%2C%20vloggers%2C%20and%20media%20moguls%20who%20are%20taking%20on%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20blowing%20past%20%E2%80%94%20the%20traditional%20entertainment%20power%20players.%20With%20a%20total%20addressable%20market%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldmansachs.com%2Finsights%2Farticles%2Fthe-creator-economy-could-approach-half-a-trillion-dollars-by-2027%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24250%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20of%202023%2C%20the%20creator%20economy%20is%20thought%20to%20account%20for%20about%2010%25%20of%20the%20global%20media%20and%20entertainment%20industry%2C%20which%20includes%20print%20media%2C%20Hollywood%2C%20gaming%2C%20music%2C%20and%20more.%20Meanwhile%2C%20moviegoing%20has%20been%20steadily%20declining%20for%20decades%20in%20the%20US%3A%20The%20attendance%20tracker%20nScreenMedia%20found%20that%20the%20average%20American%20bought%20about%20two%20movie%20tickets%20in%202023%2C%20down%20from%20five%20in%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoug%20Shapiro%2C%20a%20media%20industry%20veteran%20who's%20now%20a%20senior%20advisor%20at%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%2C%20estimates%20that%20while%20the%20creator%20media%20economy%20is%20a%20relatively%20small%20portion%20of%20the%20total%20media%20and%20entertainment%20market%2C%20it%20has%20accounted%20for%20almost%20half%20the%20market's%20growth.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20impossible%20for%20the%20traditional%20media%20players%20to%20maintain%20their%20same%20market%20share%20or%20mindshare%20in%20this%20emerging%20content%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20how%3F%20Big%20media%20companies'%20forays%20into%20building%20their%20own%20creator%20networks%20or%20making%20creator-led%20shows%20have%20largely%20been%20misses.%20(See%3A%20Disney's%20ill-fated%20acquisition%20of%20the%20YouTube%20network%20Maker%20Studios%20or%20the%20poor%20ratings%20of%20the%20NBC%20talk%20show%20hosted%20by%20the%20online%20sensation%20Lilly%20Singh.)%20And%20media%20companies%20have%20been%20distracted%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomcast-breaking-off-cable-tv-assets-msnbc-cnbc-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollapse%20of%20their%20traditional%20TV%20networks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20streaming%20profitability.%20But%20in%20a%20global%20fight%20for%20eyeballs%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20those%20of%20the%20next%20generation%20%E2%80%94%20both%20MrBeast%20and%20the%20creator%20economy%20more%20broadly%20can%20offer%20some%20lessons%20for%20traditional%20Hollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b650f09-899a-45f4-903f-fd781bddc528%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERethink%20how%20you%20reward%20talent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20their%20history%2C%20Hollywood%20companies%20have%20assumed%20all%20the%20risk%20%E2%80%94%20and%20all%20the%20reward%20%E2%80%94%20of%20making%20entertainment.%20Talent%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20was%20paid%20in%20a%20work-for-hire%20arrangement.%20Actors%20showed%20up%2C%20hit%20their%20marks%2C%20and%20let%20the%20system%20work%20its%20magic.%20This%20made%20sense%20in%20a%20time%20of%20sky-high%20costs%20just%20for%20the%20equipment%20required%20to%20get%20anything%20on%20film.%20That's%20all%20changed.%20Nowadays%2C%20anyone%20with%20an%20iPhone%20and%20a%20half-decent%20microphone%20can%20become%20a%20bona%20fide%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20like%20MrBeast%20have%20taken%20on%20more%20of%20the%20responsibility%20for%20creating%20and%20distributing%20their%20content%20directly%20to%20fans.%20Instead%20of%20being%20one%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20production%20controlled%20by%20a%20studio%2C%20they're%20the%20lead%20actor%2C%20producer%2C%20director%2C%20and%20studio%20chief.%20This%20comes%20with%20more%20risks%20if%20a%20video%20flops%2C%20but%20it%20also%20gives%20the%20new%20crop%20of%20media%20moguls%20a%20greater%20sense%20of%20ownership%20over%20their%20work.%20In%20an%20internal%20MrBeast%20production%20guidebook%2C%20which%20we%20verified%20with%20two%20former%20staffers%2C%20Donaldson%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20this%20ownership.%20%26quot%3BThis%20channel%20is%20my%20baby%2C%20and%20I've%20given%20up%20my%20life%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20He%20advised%20staffers%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20ownership%20and%20don't%20give%20your%20project%20a%20chance%20to%20fail%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BDumping%20your%20bottleneck%20on%20someone%20and%20then%20just%20walking%20away%20until%20it's%20done%20is%20lazy%2C%20and%20it%20gives%20room%20for%20error.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYouTubers%20are%20so%20attached%20to%20their%20channels%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20second%20former%20MrBeast%20staffer%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20built%20them%20through%20blood%2C%20sweat%2C%20and%20tears%20for%20decades.%26quot%3B%20The%20staffer%2C%20along%20with%20other%20ex-employees%20in%20this%20story%2C%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20protect%20business%20relationships.%20Their%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MrBeast%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e44221cfb7f307e5715bb6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThis%20channel%20is%20my%20baby%2C%20and%20I've%20given%20up%20my%20life%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Jimmy%20Donaldson%2C%20aka%20MrBeast%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20guidebook%20to%20staff.%3Cp%3EAlberto%20E.%20Rodriguez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20flood%20of%20new%20tech%20lowering%20the%20cost%20of%20content%20creation%2C%20studios%20should%20consider%20sharing%20more%20of%20the%20rewards%20with%20talent%20and%20offering%20them%20more%20developmental%20support.%20Some%20Hollywood%20A-listers%20have%20already%20begun%20to%20take%20new%20compensation%20models%20seriously%3A%20Ben%20Affleck%20and%20Matt%20Damon's%20production%20company%2C%20Artists%20Equity%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20remake%20the%20compensation%20system%20by%20giving%20performers%20less%20money%20upfront%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20potential%20larger%20share%20of%20a%20project's%20post-release%20profits%2C%20among%20other%20models.%20This%20also%20creates%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20that%20can%20prevent%20frustrated%20stars%20from%20striking%20out%20on%20their%20own%20and%20heeding%20the%20siren%20call%20of%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESharing%20some%20control%20with%20stars%20goes%20beyond%20finances.%20Creators%20who%20control%20their%20shows%20can%20get%20granular%20data%2C%20such%20as%20how%20many%20people%20subscribed%20to%20their%20channel%20and%20viewed%20and%20liked%20their%20videos%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20better%20understand%20what%20their%20audience%20is%20gravitating%20toward.%20Legacy%20media%20and%20big%20tech%20entertainment%20companies%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20keep%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-biggest-quarter-new-subscribers-ever-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etight%20grip%20on%20that%20information%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20some%20studios%20may%20eschew%20giving%20up%20that%20level%20of%20data%2C%20younger%20creators%20might%20appreciate%20more%20generous%20information%20sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cool%20thing%20about%20YouTube%20is%20they%20give%20us%20super%20detailed%20graphs%20for%20every%20video%20that%20show%20the%20exact%20second%20we%20lose%20a%20viewer%20on%20every%20single%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20Donaldson%20wrote%20in%20his%20production%20guide.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20it%20is%20production%2C%20creative%2C%20or%20editing%2C%20you%20must%20always%20know%20what%20minute%20mark%20the%20content%20you%20are%20working%20on%20is.%20If%20you%20don't%2C%20then%20you're%20not%20doing%20it%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ae03c46-207d-4dea-b1ac-dfc5c95adef4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20a%20creator-like%20approach%20to%20content%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHollywood%20is%20used%20to%20making%20a%20movie%20or%20a%20season%20of%20a%20show%20and%20then%20making%20the%20audience%20wait%20a%20year%20or%20two%20for%20the%20next%20installation%20or%20sequel.%20Take%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%2C%26quot%3B%20HBO's%20%26quot%3BGame%20of%20Thrones%26quot%3B%20spinoff%2C%20which%20was%20released%20about%20three%20years%20after%20the%20original%20series%20ended.%20That's%20not%20ideal%20for%20young%20people%20who%20have%20been%20conditioned%20by%20social%20media%20to%20have%20an%20ongoing%20connection%20with%20the%20creators%20they%20follow.%20Many%20of%20these%20new%20media%20figures%20post%20weekly%20or%20even%20daily.%20MrBeast%2C%20given%20his%20high%20production%20costs%2C%20posts%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20month%20on%20his%20main%20channel%20but%20more%20regularly%20uploads%20other%20formats%2C%20such%20as%20YouTube%20shorts.%20Corporate%20media%20must%20adapt%20to%20young%20watchers'%20voracious%20appetites%20or%20risk%20losing%20them%20as%20their%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20easiest%20place%20for%20old-school%20studios%20to%20try%20out%20this%20consistency%20is%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-reality-tv-companies-producing-unscripted-hollywood-writers-strike-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereality%20TV%20and%20game%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20two%20formats%20tailor-made%20for%20short%20clips%20and%20a%20high%20volume%20of%20content.%20Britain's%20ITV%20recently%20struck%20a%20deal%20with%20YouTube%20to%20distribute%20hundreds%20of%20hours'%20worth%20of%20shows%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BLove%20Island%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BVera.%26quot%3B%20The%20deal%20also%20called%20for%20ITV%20to%20create%20clips%2C%20compilations%2C%20and%20fan%20content%20around%20the%20shows.%20Lionsgate%20and%20Sony%20are%20licensing%20shows%20and%20movies%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgaggl-tv-gen-z-creator-startup-twitch-founders-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGaggl%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20distributes%20them%20to%20creators%20to%20watch%20with%20their%20followers%20on%20platforms%20like%20Amazon's%20Twitch.%20Adam%20Harris%2C%20a%20Gaggl%20TV%20cofounder%2C%20said%20this%20approach%20had%20been%20especially%20popular%20with%20game%20shows%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Price%20Is%20Right%26quot%3B%20that%20have%20easy-to-follow%20formats%20and%20are%20interactive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20beyond%20slicing%20and%20dicing%20existing%20shows%2C%20some%20in%20Hollywood%20are%20casting%20creators%20in%20original%20programming%2C%20blurring%20the%20distinction%20between%20social%20stars%20and%20traditional%20stars.%20Streamers%20such%20as%20Roku%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-fox-tubi-streamer-won-gen-z-grew-audience-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETubi%20are%20making%20films%20starring%20creators%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Tubi's%20%26quot%3BSidelined%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20example%2C%20includes%20the%20TikToker%20Noah%20Beck)%20that%20can%20help%20them%20connect%20with%20young%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20the%20interest%20from%20platforms%20in%20top%20creators%20has%20undergone%20a%20total%20reversal%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20David%20Freeman%2C%20head%20of%20digital%20media%20at%20CAA%2C%20the%20powerful%20talent%20agency.%20%26quot%3BFrom%202014%20to%202020%2C%20it%20was%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20get%20their%20attention.%20Now%20they%20understand%20the%20undeniable%20need%20to%20cater%20to%20Gen%20Z%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20means%20creators%20have%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20IP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20digital%20streaming%20platforms%20start%20to%20look%20like%20YouTube%2C%20with%20thumbnails%20and%20recommendations%20for%20other%20videos%2C%20traditional%20media%20will%20also%20need%20to%20embrace%20some%20of%20the%20tricks%20that%20have%20helped%20creators%20maintain%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraditional%20media%20doesn't%20think%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20if%20your%20first%2030%20seconds%20suck%2C%20people%20will%20click%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20first%20former%20MrBeast%20staffer%20said.%20They%20added%20that%20directors%20would%20have%20to%20relinquish%20some%20creative%20flexibility%20in%20order%20to%20optimize%20their%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20era%20of%20retention%20farming%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20second%20ex-MrBeast%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d636dba5-ba89-4ac6-ba6d-d0d298f56ebf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStay%20true%20to%20the%20creator%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Hollywood%20has%20occasionally%20taken%20this%20advice%20and%20cast%20social%20media%20superstars%20like%20Lilly%20Singh%20and%20the%20D'Amelios%20in%20their%20own%20shows%2C%20it%20often%20makes%20the%20mistake%20of%20trying%20to%20fit%20these%20new-school%20personalities%20into%20an%20old-school%20format%20%E2%80%94%20a%20late-night%20talk%20show%20in%20Singh's%20case%2C%20or%20reality%20in%20the%20case%20of%20%26quot%3BInside%20Eats%20with%20Rhett%20and%20Link.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20trying%20to%20bring%20in%20new%20voices%20to%20enliven%20creaky%20concepts%2C%20Hollywood%20should%20expand%20its%20notion%20of%20what%20a%20show%20can%20look%20like.%20In%202014%2C%20Jonathan%20Skogmo's%20media%20company%2C%20Jukin%20Media%2C%20sold%20a%20version%20of%20its%20popular%20YouTube%20bloopers%20show%2C%20%26quot%3BFailArmy%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20Fox.%20Skogmo%20says%20it%20worked%20because%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20copy%20the%20network%20version%20of%20the%20format%2C%20Jukin%20hewed%20to%20the%20original%20more%20unpolished%20style.%20%26quot%3BWe%20took%20what%20we%20did%20on%20YouTube%20and%20made%20a%2020-minute%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20if%20you%20bring%20a%20creator%20like%20MrBeast%20to%20a%20traditional%20platform%2C%20let%20them%20be%20themselves%20(while%20making%20sure%20their%20set%20is%20up%20to%20code).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20not%20excited%20to%20get%20in%20front%20of%20that%20camera%20and%20film%20the%20video%2C%20it's%20just%20simply%20not%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Donaldson%20wrote%20in%20his%20internal%20production%20guide.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20willing%20to%20count%20to%20one%20hundred%20thousand%2C%20bury%20myself%20alive%2C%20or%20walk%20a%20marathon%20in%20the%20world's%20largest%20pairs%20of%20shoes%20if%20I%20must.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20do%20what%20makes%20me%20happy%20and%20ultimately%20the%20viewers%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraditional%20media%20companies%20must%20also%20let%20creators%20work%20authentically%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20spending%20more%20money%20than%20a%20budget-conscious%20production%20normally%20would.%20The%20former%20MrBeast%20staffers%20described%20that%20costs-are-no-object%20attitude%20as%20central%20to%20the%20MrBeast%20growth%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20MrBeast%20team%20%26quot%3Bhold%20themselves%20accountable%20to%20making%20the%20best%20version%20of%20a%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20first%20former%20staffer%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20really%20care%20about%20doing%20shit%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EHollywood%20doesn't%20need%20to%20adopt%20the%20creator%20approach%20wholesale%20%E2%80%94%20the%20new%20school%20can%20pick%20up%20a%20few%20things%20from%20the%20old%20school%2C%20too.%20Online%20media%20stars%20are%20increasingly%20professionalizing%20their%20output%20with%20help%20from%20Hollywood-trained%20talent%20and%20riffing%20on%20tried-and-true%20entertainment%20formats%20to%20make%20shows%20that%20could%20be%20at%20home%20on%20the%20big%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20hit%20video%20inspired%20by%20the%20competition%20show%20%26quot%3BBig%20Brother%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20YouTuber%20Airrack%20invited%2025%20strangers%20to%20compete%20in%20challenges%20in%20his%20house%20over%20two%20days%3B%20it%20got%2022%20million%20views.%20And%20industry%20watchers%20say%20Amazon's%20%26quot%3BBeast%20Games%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20competition%20show%20hosted%20by%20Donaldson%20and%20his%20crew%20which%20capitalized%20on%20his%20fame%20to%20become%20the%20service's%20most-watched%20unscripted%20series%20ever%2C%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20tighter%20merging%20of%20worlds.%20Netflix%20recently%20greenlighted%20a%20season%20of%20The%20Sidemen's%20YouTube%20reality%20series%20and%20launched%20a%20show%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-signs-ms-rachel-creators-hollywood-merge-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekids%20educator%20Ms.%20Rachel%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20rare%20examples%20of%20YouTubers%20moving%20to%20a%20global%20TV%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCreators%20want%20to%20embrace%20Hollywood%20to%20a%20degree%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%26quot%3B%20CAA's%20Freeman%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20see%20more%20high-profile%20projects%20like%20'Beast%20Games'%20coming%20from%20the%20streamers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20MrBeast%20can%20teach%20Hollywood%2C%20it's%20clear%20his%20forays%20into%20traditional%20media%20are%20rubbing%20off%20on%20him.%20In%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dxf0Mli0LVgI%26t%3D1051s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Donaldson%20said%20he'd%20worked%20hard%20to%20improve%20his%20storytelling%20and%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20thought%20of%20as%20%26quot%3Bjust%20a%20YouTuber%20that%20knows%20how%20to%20manipulate%20an%20algorithm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Hollywood%2C%20to%20its%20credit%2C%20is%20starting%20to%20meet%20fans%20on%20the%20platforms%20where%20they're%20spending%20time.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-fortnite-maker-epic-games-investment-iger-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney%20recently%20invested%20in%20Epic%20Games%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20hoping%20to%20promote%20its%20famous%20characters%20to%20gamers.%20Warner%20Bros.%20has%20started%20to%20use%20the%20popular%20gaming%20platform%20Roblox%20to%20promote%20film%20releases.%20These%20experiments%20have%20been%20limited%20by%20Hollywood's%20fear%20of%20losing%20control%20of%20how%20its%20IP%20is%20portrayed%2C%20but%20it%20would%20do%20well%20to%20embrace%20young%20people's%20desire%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20content%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20ignoring%20some%20unauthorized%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lines%20between%20Hollywood%20and%20the%20creator%20economy%20are%20likely%20to%20blur%20over%20time.%20But%20as%20the%20creator%20economy%20grows%2C%20Hollywood%20must%20offer%20an%20attractive%20opportunity%20to%20creators%20or%20accept%20continued%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20question%2C%20though%2C%20is%20whether%20creators%20truly%20need%20the%20streamers%20when%20their%20audiences%20are%20overwhelmingly%20consuming%20content%20on%20platforms%20like%20YouTube%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20TikTok%2C%26quot%3B%20Freeman%20says.%20%26quot%3BTime%20will%20tell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flucia-moses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELucia%20Moses%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20media%20and%20entertainment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fgeoff-weiss%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGeoff%20Weiss%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20reporter%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20media%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fdan-whateley%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDan%20Whateley%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20reporter%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20social%20media%20and%20the%20music%20business.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-business-lessons-hollywood-media-future-tv-movies-creator-economy-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739351041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a0f9a4eb4be2fff9a3475b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-business-lessons-hollywood-media-future-tv-movies-creator-economy