0viral%2C%20is%20showing%20no%20sign%20of%20dying%20down.%20Assam%20Police%2C%20too%2C%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20in%20this%20connection%20and%20a%20team%20from%20the%20state%20has%20come%20to%20Mumbai%20as%20part%20of%20the%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApoorva%20Mukhija%20today%20visited%20Khar%20police%20station%20with%20her%20lawyer%20and%20recorded%20her%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20has%20expressed%20concern%20over%20Allahbadia's%20remarks%20and%20summoned%20him%20and%20others%20linked%20to%20the%20show%20on%20February%2017.%20%26quot%3BThese%20comments%2C%20which%20have%20sparked%20widespread%20public%20outrage%2C%20violate%20the%20dignity%20and%20respect%20owed%20to%20every%20individual%2C%20particularly%20in%20a%20society%20that%20upholds%20equality%20and%20mutual%20respect%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20panel%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20hearing%20has%20been%20scheduled%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20chairperson%20Vijaya%20Rahatkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20cyber%20cell%2C%20too%2C%20has%20filed%20a%20case%20under%20the%20IT%20Act.%20Reports%20say%20that%20notices%20are%20being%20sent%20to%20at%20least%2030%20people%20linked%20to%20the%20show%20and%20they%20would%20have%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Cyber%20Cell%20and%20record%20their%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20has%20reached%20the%20Parliament%20too.%20Shiv%20Sena%20MP%20Naresh%20Mhaske%20has%20flagged%20the%20objectionable%20comments%20and%20demanded%20censorship%20on%20OTT%20platforms.%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20has%20said%20she%20would%20raise%20the%20matter%20at%20a%20House%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20row%2C%20Allahbadia%20has%20issued%20an%20apology.%20%26quot%3BMy%20comment%20was%20not%20appropriate%2C%20and%20not%20even%20funny%2C%20comedy%20is%20not%20my%20forte%2C%20I%20am%20just%20here%20to%20say%20sorry.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20he%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Blapse%20in%20my%20