excitement%20as%20the%20photo%20went%20viral.%20Many%20took%20to%20the%20comments%20section%20to%20share%20their%20thoughts%20on%20the%20meeting%2C%20with%20some%20users%20suggesting%20that%20the%20two%20tech%20leaders%20should%20collaborate%20to%20create%20the%20ultimate%20search%20engine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BGoogle%20has%20funds%2C%20and%20you%20have%20the%20best%20team%20to%20work%20on%20and%20better%20AI%20for%20humanity%20not%20just%20for%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BDid%20you%20ask%20him%20if%20he%20switched%20from%20Google%20Assistant%20to%20Perplexity%20Assistant%20on%20his%20Apple%20phone%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0A%20third%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLooks%20like%20an%20incredible%20moment!%20Must've%20been%20a%20great%20conversation.%26quot%3B%20A%20fourth%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BChennai%20Express%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20a%20fifth%20quipped%2C%20%26quot%3BDid%20you%20speak%20in%20Tamil%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20Mr%20Pichai%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparis-ai-summit-google-ceo-sundar-pichai-meets-pm-modi-in-paris-7689823%5C%22%3Emet%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20highlighted%20the%20%26quot%3Bincredible%20opportunities%26quot%3B%20that%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20will%20bring%20to%20India.%C2%A0The%20Alphabet%20CEO%20also%20noted%20the%20potential%20for%20close%20collaboration%20between%20Google%20and%20India%20to%20advance%20the%20country's%20digital%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20Delighted%20to%20meet%20with%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20while%20in%20Paris%20for%20the%20AI%20Action%20Summit.%20We%20discussed%20the%20incredible%20opportunities%20AI%20will%20bring%20to%20India%20and%20ways%20we%20can%20work%20closely%20together%20on%20India's%20digital%20transformation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%C2%A0Mr%20Pichai%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Google%20and%20Alphabet%2C%20leading%20the%20company's%20innovation%20and%20growth%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%20Born%20in%20Madurai%2C%20Mr%20Pichai%20has%20risen%20through%20the%20ranks%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20tech%20leaders%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Aravind%20Srinivas%20is%20the%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Perplexity%20AI%2C%20a%20cutting-edge%20AI-powered%20search%20engine%20backed%20by%20prominent%20investors%2C%20including%20Jeff%20Bezos.%20Founded%20in%202022%2C%20Perplexity%20AI%20was%20established%20by%20Srinivas%20alongside%20Andy%20Konwinski%2C%20Denis%20Yarats%2C%20and%20Johnny%20Ho.%20A%20distinguished%20alumnus%20of%20IIT-Madras%2C%20Srinivas%20earned%20his%20PhD%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%20His%20career%20began%20as%20a%20research%20intern%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20followed%20by%20stints%20at%20Google%20and%20DeepMind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739345280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F64ev2g3g_-sundar-pichai-with-aravind-srinivas_625x300_12_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchennai-express-sundar-pichai-meets-aravind-srinivas-in-paris-pic-goes-viral-7691967%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Both%20CEOs%20were%20in%20Paris%20to%20attend%20the%20AI%20Action%20Summit%2C%20a%20gathering%20of%20global%20leaders%2C%20tech%20executives%2C%20and%20lawmakers%20focused%20on%20shaping%20the%20future%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchennai-express-sundar-pichai-meets-aravind-srinivas-in-paris-pic-goes-viral-7691967%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dumbbells%20Hung%20From%20Private%20Parts%3A%20Ragging%20Horror%20At%20Kerala%20Medical%20College%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStripped%20naked%2C%20dumbbells%20hung%20from%20private%20parts%2C%20stabbed%20with%20geometry%20box%20compasses%20and%20beaten%20bloody%20for%20three%20months%20-%20a%20fresh%20ragging%20incident%20has%20rocked%20a%20government%20college%20in%20Kerala%20where%20five%20third-year%20nursing%20students%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20subjecting%20their%20juniors%20to%20months%20of%20brutal%20physical%20and%20mental%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20at%20Government%20Nursing%20College%20in%20Kottayam%20where%20three%20first-year%20students%20-%20all%20from%20Thiruvananthapuram%20-%C2%A0%20filed%20a%20formal%20complaint%20with%20the%20Kottayam%20Gandhinagar%20police%2C%20detailing%20a%20series%20of%20violent%20acts%20that%20began%20in%20November%202024%20and%20continued%20for%20nearly%20three%20months.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20led%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20students%20and%20their%20arrest%20under%20the%20Anti-Ragging%20Act.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20first-year%20students%20were%20forced%20to%20stand%20naked%20while%20their%20seniors%20hung%20dumbbells%20from%20their%20private%20parts.%20The%20victims%20were%20also%20subjected%20to%20injuries%20using%20sharp%20objects%2C%20including%20a%20compass%20from%20a%20geometry%20box.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cruelty%20did%20not%20stop%20there.%20Lotion%20was%20applied%20to%20the%20wounds%2C%20causing%20pain.%20When%20the%20victims%20screamed%20in%20agony%2C%20the%20lotion%20was%20forcibly%20smeared%20into%20their%20mouths.%20The%20seniors%20allegedly%20filmed%20these%20acts%20and%20threatened%20the%20juniors%20with%20dire%20consequences%2C%20including%20jeopardising%20their%20academic%20futures%2C%20if%20they%20dared%20to%20report%20the%20abuse.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20also%20claims%20that%20the%20seniors%20regularly%20extorted%20money%20from%20the%20juniors%20on%20Sundays%20to%20buy%20alcohol.%20Those%20who%20refused%20to%20comply%20were%20beaten.%20One%20student%2C%20unable%20to%20bear%20the%20harassment%20any%20longer%2C%20informed%20his%20father%2C%20who%20then%20encouraged%20him%20to%20approach%20the%20police.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20five%20are%20currently%20in%20police%20custody%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20produced%20before%20a%20magistrate%20by%20Wednesday%20afternoon.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20weeks%20after%20a%2015-year-old%20schoolboy%20in%20Kochi%20died%20by%20suicide.%20The%20student's%20mother%20alleged%20that%20her%20son%20was%20bullied%20by%20students%20which%20pushed%20him%20towards%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739345280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ftrfr9ni_kerala-ragging-row-_625x300_12_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-ragging-dumbbells-hung-from-private-parts-ragging-horror-at-kerala-medical-college-7691484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fresh%20ragging%20incident%20has%20rocked%20a%20government%20college%20in%20Kerala%20where%20five%20third-year%20nursing%20students%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20subjecting%20their%20juniors%20to%20months%20of%20brutal%20physical%20and%20mental%20abuse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-ragging-dumbbells-hung-from-private-parts-ragging-horror-at-kerala-medical-college-7691484%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women%20lead%20in%20over%20half%20of%20Hollywood%20movies%20for%20first%20time%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739344988000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118167862%2Cimgsize-1025411.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwomen-lead-in-over-half-of-hollywood-movies-for-first-time%2Farticleshow%2F118167519.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%2