CK%20T.%20FALLON%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20US%20Army%20Photo%20by%20Bridgett%20Siter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPalmer%20Luckey's%20Anduril%20is%20set%20to%20take%20over%20Microsoft's%20US%20Army%20contract%20for%20mixed-reality%20goggles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2010-year%20contract%2C%20worth%20%2422%20billion%2C%20has%20been%20plagued%20by%20development%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnduril%20now%20has%20a%20shot%20%E2%80%94%20a%20moment%20that%20Luckey%20said%20was%20part%20of%20Anduril's%20original%20vision.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPalmer%20Luckey%20just%20clinched%20a%20big%20personal%20win%20%E2%80%94%20his%20defense%20startup%2C%20Anduril%2C%20is%20set%20to%20take%20over%20Microsoft's%20%2422%20billion%20contract%20to%20make%20high-tech%20goggles%20for%20the%20US%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20firms%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.microsoft.com%2F2025%2F02%2F11%2Fanduril-and-microsoft-partner-to-advance-integrated-visual-augmentation-system-ivas-program-for-the-u-s-army%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20transition%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20saying%20Anduril%20would%20spearhead%20%26quot%3Boversight%20of%20production%2C%20future%20development%20of%20hardware%20and%20software%2C%20and%20delivery%20timelines%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-uses-futuristic-heads-up-display-to-fight-coronavirus-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIntegrated%20Visual%20Augmentation%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IVAS%20is%20meant%20to%20give%20soldiers%20a%20headset%20that%20uses%20augmented%20and%20visual%20reality%20to%20feed%20them%20information%20on%20the%20battlefield%20in%20real%20time.%20One%20of%20its%20most%20important%20functions%20is%20to%20help%20the%20wearer%20identify%20drones%20quickly%20and%20clearly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Luckey%2C%20the%20contract%20transition%20is%20his%20own%20watershed%20moment.%20In%20his%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpalmerluckey.com%2Fturning-soldiers-into-superheroes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Tuesday%2C%20he%20wrote%20that%20the%20announcement%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20personal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20I've%20done%20in%20my%20career%20%E2%80%94%20building%20Oculus%20out%20of%20a%20camper%20trailer%2C%20shipping%20VR%20to%20millions%20of%20consumers%2C%20getting%20run%20out%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%20by%20backstabbing%20snakes%2C%20betting%20that%20Anduril%20could%20tear%20people%20out%20of%20the%20bigtech%20megacorp%20matrix%20and%20put%20them%20to%20work%20on%20our%20nation's%20most%20important%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20has%20led%20to%20this%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20calls%20back%20to%20Luckey's%20original%20foray%20into%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20when%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-palmer-luckey%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520founder%2520of%2520Oculus%2520and%2520Anduril%26amp%3Btext%3DPalmer%2520Luckey%2520founded%2520the%2520virtual%2Cdefense%252Dtech%2520startup%2520Anduril%2520Industries.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efounded%20Oculus%20VR%20and%20sold%20it%20to%20Facebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202014%20for%20%242%20billion.%20After%20being%20ousted%20from%20Facebook%2C%20he%20started%20Anduril%20in%202017%2C%20and%20his%20defense%20startup%20has%20since%20delved%20into%20drones%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20counter-electronic%20warfare%20systems%20for%20the%20US%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Microsoft%20and%20Anduril%20said%20they%20were%20collaborating%20on%20the%20IVAS%20program%2C%20with%20Luckey's%20firm%20providing%20its%20Lattice%20software%20for%20the%20headsets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20entire%20program%20is%20set%20to%20be%20under%20Anduril's%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckey%20wrote%20in%20his%20blog%20that%20he'd%20recognized%20the%20combat%20potential%20for%20high-tech%20goggles%20since%20he%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20and%20that%20providing%20them%20to%20the%20US%20military%20was%20part%20of%20Anduril's%20original%20pitch%20deck%20eight%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20Anduril's%20size%20at%20the%20time%2C%20which%20he%20estimated%20was%20a%20team%20of%20about%20a%20dozen%20people%2C%20hurt%20its%20chances%20at%20scoring%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20believe%20our%20crazy%20pitch%20could%20have%20won%20this%20from%20the%20start%20%E2%80%94%20as%20things%20stand%2C%20though%2C%20there%20is%20no%20time%20like%20the%20present%2C%26quot%3B%20Luckey%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb33f52c-1dbf-43c7-9c55-059c6f731db0%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20Army%20is%20having%20a%20rough%20time%20with%20IVAS%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20handover%20still%20needs%20to%20be%20approved%20by%20the%20US%20government.%20The%20US%20Army%20awarded%20Microsoft%20the%2010-year%20contract%20in%202021%2C%20when%20the%20deal%20was%20valued%20at%20up%20to%20%2422%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IVAS%20program%20has%20since%20faced%20a%20tough%20road%20in%20development%20and%20testing.%20Microsoft%20converted%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-lost-billions-hololens-ivas-contract-trouble-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHoloLens%202%20headsets%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20military%20use%2C%20but%20soldiers%20criticized%20the%20devices%2C%20complaining%20of%20software%20glitches%20and%20side%20effects%20like%20headaches%2C%20nausea%2C%20and%20neck%20strain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20solder%20wearing%20a%20headset%20kneeling%20and%20aiming%20a%20gun.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6065dc6b6183e10019819bc1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20Army%20soldier%20wearing%20a%20prototype%20IVAS%20headset.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feedback%20prompted%20the%20US%20Army%20to%20delay%20the%20IVAS%20program%20in%20October%202021%2C%20and%20the%20systems%20have%20been%20repeatedly%20retweaked%20for%20the%20battlefield%20in%20the%20years%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20Microsoft%2C%20the%20entire%20HoloLens%20project%20appeared%20to%20be%20ailing.%20Business%20Insider's%20Ashley%20Stewart%20reported%20in%202022%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-hololens-3-metaverse-mixed-reality-strategy-confusion-rivalries-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplans%20for%20a%20third%20version%20of%20the%20headset%20were%20scrapped%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20the%20company%20had%20lost%20billions%20on%20its%20mixed-reality%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202024%2C%20Microsoft%20confirmed%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-lost-billions-hololens-ivas-contract-trouble-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehalt%20production%20of%20the%20HoloLens%202%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cut%20support%20for%20the%20device%2C%20throwing%20the%20IVAS%20program%20into%20question.%20Microsoft's%20move%20tracked%20with%20a%20shift%20in%20the%20entire%20industry%2C%20as%20tech%20giants%20stepped%20back%20from%20developing%20mixed-reality%20headsets%20to%20instead%20focus%20on%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Microsoft's%20decision%2C%20the%20US%20Army%20hinted%20in%20late%20January%20that%20it%20was%20surveying%20the%20market%20for%20a%20new%20contender%20for%20its%2010-year%20contract%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsam.gov%2Fopp%2Fb45e66c680f240e29098fe3a377721ed%2Fview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereleasing%20a%20request%20for%20information%3C%2Fa%3E%20related%20to%20the%20IVAS%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Anduril%20now%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%2C%20it's%20not%20immediately%20clear%20what%20hardware%20it%20will%20use%20for%20the%20IVAS.%20There%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20th