20workers%20to%20relocate%20owing%20to%20availability%20of%20government%20welfare%20schemes.%20This%20comes%20week%20after%20his%2090-hour%20work%20week%20remark%20led%20to%20a%20widespread%20debate%20about%20work-life%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Subrahmanyan%2C%20while%20speaking%20at%20the%20CII's%20Mystic%20South%20Global%20Linkages%20Summit%202025%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20said%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20get%20workers%20for%20the%20construction%20industry%20as%20they%20are%20reluctant%20to%20travel%20from%20their%20hometown%20due%20to%20a%20preference%20for%20comfort.%20He%20said%20that%20schemes%20like%20MGNREGA%2C%20direct%20benefit%20transfers%20and%20JAN%20DHAN%20accounts%20likely%20affect%20labour%20mobilisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLabour%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20move%20for%20opportunities.%20Maybe%20their%20local%20economy%20is%20doing%20well%2C%20maybe%20it%20is%20due%20to%20the%20various%20government%20schemes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20shortage%20of%20labour%20would%20impact%20the%20building%20of%20India's%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Subrahmanyan%20also%20said%20India%20faces%20the%20peculiar%20problem%20of%20migration%2C%20with%20L%26amp%3BT%20requiring%204%20lakh%20workers%2C%20but%20recruiting%2016%20lakh%20people%20owing%20to%20attrition.%20He%20also%20raised%20the%20need%20to%20revise%20wages%20for%20workers%20in%20sync%20with%20inflation%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20Middle%20East%20draws%20workers%20as%20it%20draws%20three%20to%203.5%20times%20the%20salary%20they%20draw%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20Chairman%20had%20said%20last%20month%20that%20he%20wants%20his%20employees%20to%20work%20on%20Sundays%20too.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20do%20sitting%20at%20home%3F%20How%20long%20can%20you%20stare%20at%20your%20wife%3F%20Come%20on%2C%20get%20to%20the%20office%20and%20start%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20works%20on%20Sundays%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20saw%20many%20industry%20leaders%20like%20Adar%20Poonawalla%2C%20Anand%20Mahindra%20and%20ITC's%20Sanjiv%20Puri%2C%20advocating%20the%20need%20for%20work-life%20balance%20for%20productivity.%20The%20matter%20reached%20the%20Parliament%20when%20the%20government%20told%20Parliament%20last%20week%20that%20it%20is%20not%20considering%20any%20proposal%20to%20increase%20the%20maximum%20working%20hours%20to%2070%20or%2090%20hours%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20discourse%20over%2070-90-hour%20work%20week%2C%20pre-Budget%20Economic%20Survey%20on%20Friday%20last%20had%20cited%20studies%20to%20state%20that%20spending%20over%2060%20hours%20a%20week%20on%20work%20could%20have%20adverse%20health%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20noted%20that%20spending%20long%20hours%20at%20one's%20desk%20is%20detrimental%20to%20mental%20well-being%2C%20and%20individuals%20who%20spend%2012%20or%20more%20hours%20(per%20day)%20at%20a%20desk%20have%20distressed%20or%20struggling%20levels%20of%20mental%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739337000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fi8mncg4o_sn-subrahmanyan_625x300_10_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-90-hour-work-week-l-t-chief-kicks-up-workers-reluctance-row-7691123%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SN%20Subrahmanyan%20said%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20get%20workers%20for%20the%20construction%20industry%20as%20they%20are%20reluctant%20to%20travel%20from%20their%20hometown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-90-hour-work-week-l-t-chief-kicks-up-workers-reluctance-row-7691123%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDisrespecting%20Identity%20Not%20Fun%26quot%3B%3A%20Elvish%20Yadav's%20Remarks%20On%20Actor%20Spark%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%2