led%20and%20the%20video%20was%20eventually%20pulled%20off%20by%20YouTube%20back%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20incident%2C%20Aamir%20Khan%2C%20at%20the%20Youth%20for%20Governance%202015%20event%2C%20said%20he%20believes%20in%20freedom%20of%20speech%20but%20he%20didn't%20support%20%26quot%3Bverbal%20violence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Karan%20(Johar)%20and%20Arjun%20(Kapoor)%20told%20me%20what%20they%20said%20and%20did%20as%20part%20of%20the%20'roast'%2C%20I%20felt%20it%20was%20very%20violent%20event.%20I%20completely%20believe%20in%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20no%20issues%20there.%20Violence%20is%20not%20always%20physical%2C%20it%20can%20be%20emotional%2C%20it%20can%20be%20verbal.%20Jab%20aap%20kisi%20ko%20insult%20karte%20ho%20to%20aap%20violence%20perpetuate%20kar%20rahe%20ho%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Internet%20argued%20for%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20the%20other%20section%20didn't%20approve%20of%20the%20language%20of%20%26quot%3Broasting.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20Joining%20the%20bandwagon%20of%20detractors%2C%20Aamir%20Khan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20has%20the%20right%20to%20air%20their%20opinions.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20it%20was%20not%20funny.%20I%20am%20not%20a%20kid%20that%20I%20will%20laugh%20listening%20to%20abuses.%20I%20am%20way%20past%20that%20age.%20I%20scolded%20both%20Karan%20and%20Arjun%2C%20who%20are%20my%20friends%2C%20and%20told%20them%20that%20I%20do%20not%20find%20it%20funny%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20impress%20me%2C%20try%20making%20me%20laugh%20without%20insulting%20anyone.%20I%20will%20enjoy%20it%20then.%20I%20am%20not%20talking%20about%20AIB%2C%20but%20about%20Arjun%2C%20Karan%20and%20other%20actors%20at%20the%20event...I%20think%20as%20a%20creative%20person%2C%20it%20is%20my%20responsibility%20to%20search%20for%20the%20good%20in%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Cem%3ELagaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20actor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22740%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FBollyBlindsNGossip%2Fcomments%2F1imq228%2Fthrowback_to_an_old_video_of_aamir_khan_sharing%2F%5C%22%3EThrowback%20to%20an%20old%20video%20of%20Aamir%20Khan%20sharing%20his%20views%20on%20freedom%20of%20speech%20!%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnby%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2FAuthorityBrain%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2FAuthorityBrain%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FBollyBlindsNGossip%2F%5C%22%3EBollyBlindsNGossip%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanveer%20Allahbadia's%20comment%20sparked%20reactions%20from%20Imtiaz%20Ali%2C%20Manoj%20Bajpayee.%20B%20Praak%20has%20already%20cancelled%20his%20scheduled%20appearance%20on%20Ranveer's%20podcast%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanveer%20Allahbadia%20and%20others%2C%20including%20comedian%20Samay%20Raina%20and%20the%20producers%20of%20the%20stand-up%20comedy%20show%20%3Cem%3EIndia's%20Got%20Latent%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20have%20been%20summoned%20-%20on%20February%2017%20-%20by%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20over%20derogatory%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20when%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20had%20asked%20a%20contestant%2C%20%26quot%3BWould%20you%20rather%20watch%20your%20parents%20have%20sex%20every%20day%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20life%20or%20join%20in%20once%20and%20stop%20it%20forever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20police%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20the%2031-year-old%20podcaster%20along%20with%20Ashish%20Chanchlani%2C%20Jaspreet%20Singh%2C%20Apoorva%20Makhija%20and%20Samay%20Raina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20backlash%2C%20Allahbadia%2C%20who%20has%204.5%20million%20followers%20on%20Instagram%20and%201.05%20crore%20YouTube%20subscribers%2C%20issued%20an%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20message%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20shouldn't%20have%20