%20process%20began%20with%20the%20development%20of%20a%20cutting%20machine%2C%20which%20was%20designed%20to%20shred%20the%20cigarette%20stub%20fibres%20into%20small%20pieces.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20cutting%20process%20takes%20less%20than%2030%20seconds%20for%20each%20batch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391091%2Fbliss-natural-bio-based-pads-kenaf-fashion-technology-startup-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efibres%20are%20cut%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20formed%20into%20a%20pulp%2C%20we%20use%20biodegradable%20chemicals%20to%20treat%20them%20and%20this%20process%20takes%20around%2024%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20elaborates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FPicture-3_11zon-1738856245-500x750.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Naman%20Gupta%20is%20the%20main%20visionary%20behind%20the%20idea%20of%20turning%20cigarette%20butts%20to%20eco-friendly%20toys%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FPicture-3_11zon-1738856245-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FPicture-3_11zon-1738856245-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FPicture-3_11zon-1738856245-768x1152.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FPicture-3_11zon-1738856245-1024x1536.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FPicture-3_11zon-1738856245-1365x2048.jpg%201365w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FPicture-3_11zon-1738856245-1200x1800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%