time.%20By%20combining%20these%20steps%2C%20the%20device%20is%20helping%20save%20labour%20and%20improve%20accuracy%20in%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-1-1738222588.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kahan%20Singh%20is%20bringing%20hope%20with%20his%20new%20method%20of%20growing%20paddy%20that%20reduces%20water%20usage%20to%2025%20percent.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-1-1738222588.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-1-1738222588-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-1-1738222588-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-1-1738222588-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-1-1738222588-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-401984%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKahan%20Singh%20is%20bringing%20hope%20with%20his%20new%20method%20of%20growing%20paddy%20that%20reduces%20water%20usage%20by%2075%20percent.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20it%20works%2C%20the%20retired%20officer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20machine%20prepares%20the%20beds%20in%20the%20field%20and%20simultaneously%20plants%20the%20seeds%20on%20the%20bed.%20So%2C%20after%20we%20plough%20the%20field%2C%20we%20let%20the%20machine%20do%20the%20work.%20When%20the%20seeds%20germinate%2C%20we%20supply%20water%20only%20in%20the%20furrows%20of%20the%20beds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20bed%20width%20is%20about%20two%20feet%20and%20the%20furrow%20width%20is%20one%20foot%2C%20water%20is%20supplied%20in%20these%20furrows%20only%20when%20needed.%20This%20method%20ensures%20water%20reaches%20the%20roots%20without%20submerging%20the%20entire%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20this%20technique%20requires%20only%2025%20percent%20of%20the%20water%20traditionally%20used%20for%20paddy%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransitioning%20from%20conventional%20methods%20to%20SRB%20was%20not%20without%20its%20challenges.%20The%20technology%20had%20to%20address%20one%20major%20problem%3A%20effective%20weed%20control%20without%20a%20constant%20layer%20of%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20tendency%20for%20weeds%20to%20germinate%20along%20with%20paddy.%20Weeds%20can%20severely%20affect%20paddy%20growth%20by%20competing%20with%20it%20for%20water%20and%20nutrients.%20This%20is%20why%20farmers%20flood%20paddy%20fields%20to%20kill%20weeds.%20To%20overcome%20this%2C%20we%20use%20herbicide-tolerant%20seeds%2C%20which%20have%20been%20given%20to%20us%20by%20the%20Indian%20Agricultural%20Research%20Institute.%20Once%20the%20seeds%20kill%20the%20weeds%2C%20paddy%20thrives%20within%20about%20100%20days.%20My%20experience%20with%20this%20technique%20has%20been%20wonderful%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20growing%20season%2C%20the%20SRB%20technique%20was%20adopted%20at%2012%20trial%20sites%20across%20Punjab%2C%20showing%20great%20results%20in%20both%20water%20conservation%20and%20crop%20production.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20yield%20was%20on%20par%20with%20traditional%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kahan%20Singh%2C%20who%20harvested%2028%20quintals%20of%20paddy%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%20water%2C%20scripting%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaswinder%20Singh%2C%20a%20farmer%20and%20resident%20of%20Lambra%20village%20in%20the%20Hoshiarpur%20district%2C%20adopted%20the%20SRB%20technique%20last%20season%20to%20grow%20paddy%20on%20two%20acres%20of%20land.%20%E2%80%9CI%20observed%20that%20using%20this%20technique%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20save%20Rs%208%2C000%20per%20acre%20on%20irrigation%20and%20labour%20costs.%20As%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20standing%20water%20in%20this%20method%2C%20I%20only%20had%20to%20water%20my%20field%20four%20times.%20Earlier%2C%20we%20had%20to%20irrigate%20the%20field%20at%20least%2020%20times.%20Despite%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F143975%2Fdrip-irrigation-increases-rice-yield-of-tamil-nadu-farmers%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless%20irrigation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20no%20difference%20in%20the%20yield%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20farmer%2C%20who%20harvested%2024%20quintals%20of%20rice%20from%20his%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-3-1738222596.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Last%20season%2C%20Kahan%20Singh's%20method%20was%20adopted%20at%2012%20trial%20sites%20across%20Punjab.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-3-1738222596.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-3-1738222596-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-3-1738222596-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-3-1738222596-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fias-paddy-farming-less-water-3-1738222596-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-401985%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELast%20season%2C%20Kahan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20method%20was%20adopted%20at%2012%20trial%20sites%20across%20Punjab.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20increasing%20water%20shortage%20in%20his%20village%2C%20Jaswinder%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20depend%20on%20tubewells%20for%20water.%20Every%20year%2C%20we%20have%20to%20install%20more%20powerful%20motors%20to%20extract%20groundwater%2C%20which%20has%20now%20dropped%20to%20a%20depth%20of%20280%20feet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20this%20technique%20will%20greatly%20help%20farmers%20get%20the%20same%20yield%20from%20the%20same%20land%20while%20reducing%20irrigation%20and%20labour%20costs.%20More%20importantly%2C%20we%20will%20be%20saving%20so%20much%20groundwater.%20Usually%2C%20farmers%20fear%20doing%20experiments%2C%20but%20I%20hope%20that%20seeing%20my%20success%2C%20more%20farmers%20will%20adopt%20this%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Jaswinder%2C%20who%20plans%20to%20expand%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F243086%2Fhow-to-grow-rice-at-home-bottles-planting-seedlings-kerala-couple-paddy-terrace-farming-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaddy%20cultivation%20%3C%2Fa%3Eusing%20Kahan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20technique%20to%20four%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20financial%20benefits%20of%20SRB%20are%20clear.%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20save%20approximately%20Rs%208%2C000%20per%20acre%20due%20to%20reduced%20labour%20and%20water%20requirements%2C%20slashing%20their%20cultivation%20costs%20by%20nearly%20half.%20These%20savings%20make%20the%20technique%20attractive%20for%20adoption%20across%20the%20economically%20stressed%20farming%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20Kahan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20success%2C%20other%20local%20farmers%20are%20eager%20to%20try%20the%20method.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20plan%20to%20expand%20usage%20to%20larger%20areas%20next%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20work%20is%20more%20than%20a%20fleeting%20innovation%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20revolutionise%20farming%20in%20water-scarce%20areas.%20Reflecting%20on%20his%20early%20years%2C%20he%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20so%20many%20cherished%20childhood%20memories%20in%20my%20village%3B%20so%20many%20stories%20revolve%20around%20wells.%20I%20have%20seen%20people%20take%20their%20livestock%20to%20those%20wells%2C%20bathe%2C%20and%20fetch%20water.%20Today%2C%20functioning%20wells%20are%20nowhere%20in%20sight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20foster%20a%20new%20mindset%20among%20farmers%20toward%20regenerative%20and%20conservation-oriented%20agriculture%20so%20that%20we%20can%20ensure%20Punjab%20remains%20robustly%20productive%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kahan%20Singh%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20former%20IAS%20officer%20continues%20to%20inspire%20change%2C%20his%20vision%20for%20a%20more%20sustainable%20Punjab%20is%20a%20strong%20reminder%20that%20innovative%20solutions%20to%20global%20challenges%20can%20start%20in%20a%20single%20villag